    "description": "Grow your career with Meesho Logistics Ventures Solutions! We are hiring a Distribution Manager for our Ludhiana team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Meesho Logistics Ventures Solutions:\nMeesho Logistics Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ludhiana, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Meesho Logistics Ventures Solutions!",
